{"tid":1613570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚班狗玩無警時份？","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T14:48:52.000Z","uid":199235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e58976a45e019d8865fac40b6c444fcc74936815","tid":1613570,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"今晚突發片地開花，見到手足為民除害，係政府告訴我地和平示威係無用既，加上神獸降臨各區，當然十分高興。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最希望手足今晚平安回家，但奇怪居然咁耐見唔到半隻狗？佢地無理由唔知出面發生咩事，尤其黃大仙咁近狗屋，我懷疑班狗有心任由抗爭者做佢地想做既事，我相信唔係未有準備而人手唔夠，我估係相玩學721咁，今次任由抗爭者&ldquo;破壞&rdquo;變所以&ldquo;暴途&rdquo;希望可以民意逆轉，等市民覺得警暴對付抗爭者係合理？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但佢地萬萬估唔到香港人去到今時今日已經真係核彈到唔割，加上警犬開始用槍射殺抗爭者，佢地睇左四個月警犬既不公義畫面，都係個句唔支持既點都唔會支持，我相信大部份支持抗爭市民睇到只會覺得有種興奮湧上心頭，莫講話割蓆了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b429622c8886c97336fd4a83cd336d45511bbd","tid":1613570,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c9d5fcac2c7fc4bcf2b2d1ac713ad0a610d9a9","tid":1613570,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"唔好諗到佢地有腦 多區開花出唔切"}]}